{"tid":905870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"桐谷美玲同框荷里活男神 網友傻眼「這是新垣結衣吧」","createTime":"2018-11-17T13:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T12:21:18.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9e567d585427bb58e1e24c83b43f50fea2ad64fb","tid":905870,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"日本女星桐谷美玲因演出《花樣少年少女》、《有喜歡的人》而走紅，甜美外型大受粉絲歡迎。日前桐谷在IG貼出與奧斯卡影帝的合照，卻被認為撞臉新垣結衣，意外掀起話題。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/11/15/phpC4xRMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2FphpC4xRMt.jpg&h=23b49083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n桐谷美玲（左）同框艾迪瑞德曼。<br />\n<br />\n桐谷美玲為電影《怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行》日本區宣傳大使，受邀飛往英國出席倫敦首映會，在IG貼出與主角艾迪瑞德曼的合照。艾迪曾以《愛的萬物論》成為奧斯卡影帝，前者建基於Sport Series的570S車系，內外全面強化，這也讓桐谷秒變小粉絲，直呼太光榮。但卻有不少人把焦點放在這張照片桐谷似乎撞臉新垣結衣，表示「本來不覺得她們像，但這張真的認錯」、「我的老婆們竟合而為一了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/11/15/php260Usy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2Fphp260Usy.jpg&h=5b4c465f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新垣結衣也曾被誤認是桐谷美玲。<br />\n<br />\n其實過去新垣結衣在電影《乒乓少女大逆襲》的宣傳照也被不少人認成桐谷美玲，新垣更透露某次看到桐谷的雜誌封面，竟想說「咦？那是我嗎」，仔細一看才發現自己也認錯，可見兩人的相似度的確很高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjwEZSO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjwEZSO.png&h=476dda5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n桐谷美玲（右）與新垣結衣有些神似。"},{"pid":"620ac52e5d0810e538898c46e1afe378b3260133","tid":905870,"uid":34561,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"艾迪曾以《愛的萬物論》成為奧斯卡影帝，前者建基於Sport Series的570S車系，內外全面強化，這也讓桐谷秒變小粉絲"},{"pid":"8505f9583b7491e3ac30a9c13ffbd95a586ac217","tid":905870,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"60eb45409745a8f46e089244f634924d409738c8","tid":905870,"uid":49197,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"新垣結衣同桐谷美玲都係頂級靚女"},{"pid":"ef891d80c1a5a68b3e4a5e975a8eef3aec706478","tid":905870,"uid":40575,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"朱千雪黎喎"},{"pid":"ff7c0ed3c6be37b2f47b853a2e99e6002fa9f0ed","tid":905870,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2d2da3169a5d1f0219e9488ec65001e7bf4394","tid":905870,"uid":47147,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d5b751915731822f59959cca12a004fc2d74cfc","tid":905870,"uid":54959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"每次睇樓主啲post 都好期待內文攝啲咩新聞入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc13a786cf52831905077f729c3fed710bff72d","tid":905870,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n朱千雪靚D喔"},{"pid":"faa514201ba1da6606d189bc3e12164615846c74","tid":905870,"uid":157872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"植入得好自然，留意唔到千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似依個post咁 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/770832/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/770832/page/1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5c72a3645d72ff2bfd349b4d95d64218043751","tid":905870,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"桐谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8943a94f98b9e83360085eb1194162396701fd82","tid":905870,"uid":72926,"lik